== Father son Nobel Laureates ==
There are six not four father son pairs of Nobel Laureates as listed on both wikipedia.org and nobelprize.org  <small class="autosigned">—&nbsp;Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/117.203.148.224|117.203.148.224]] ([[User talk:117.203.148.224|talk]]) 16:24, 31 August 2015 (UTC)</small><!-- Template:Unsigned IP --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->
:But only four won the Nobel Prize in Physics. The other were [[Hans von Euler-Chelpin]] (chemistry, 1929) and [[Ulf von Euler]] (medicine, 1970) and [[Arthur Kornberg]] (medicine, 1969) and [[Roger D. Kornberg]] (chemistry, 2006). [[User:Hawkeye7|Hawkeye7]] ([[User talk:Hawkeye7|talk]]) 19:36, 31 August 2015 (UTC)
